room_title: Escape room "The King's Treasure" by Urban Escape Games in Atlanta
room_address: 1800 Sandy Plains, Industrial Pkwy Ste. 320, Marietta, GA 30066
room_description: The King has arranged a treasure hunt for all of his princes and princesses. Unfortunately, he was called away last minute to help hunt a dragon that has been wreaking havoc on his Kingdom. You are on your own to search the castle for the hidden treasure. Figure out the clues, work the puzzles and find keys and codes to the many locks on the way to the final locked golden treasure chest!
